import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"react-native-projects"}}>{`React Native Projects`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"starting-from-scratch-using-paragon"}}>{`Starting from scratch using Paragon`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Open up the Paragon, Paragon Server and Design System repos.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"design-system"}}>{`Design System`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-bash"}}>{`yarn storybook # starts storybook with components on 6006
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"paragon"}}>{`Paragon`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-bash"}}>{`yarn start # start up Paragon
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h3" components={components} props={{"id":"paragon-server"}}>{`Paragon Server`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-bash"}}>{`node index.local.js # start the server
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"directions"}}>{`Directions`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ol" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Use Storybook to select the components/fonts that you want.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Use Paragon to write in what you need with initial state.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Create the project using the Paragon Server.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Use the returned Github URL to clone down the built website.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ol">{`Follow the run-paragon phase detailed in the following section.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"run-paragon-phase"}}>{`Run Paragon phase`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="pre" components={components}><MDXTag name="code" components={components} parentName="pre" props={{"className":"language-shell"}}>{`#!/bin/bash
git clone \$1
cd \$1
run-paragon #runs lift, shotgun, fonts etc
yarn start
`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
